# ğŸ›¡ï¸ CyberShield Web Security Scanner

CyberShield is a modern web security scanner built with **Flask** and a sleek **radar-style UI**. It scans websites for common vulnerabilities (like SQL Injection, XSS, and missing security headers) and presents results in a **detailed, tech-savvy, and user-friendly dashboard**.

---

## âš¡ Features

- Input any URL and run a security scan.
- Animated **radar and progress bar** during scanning.
- **Results Dashboard** with:
  - Vulnerability summary
  - Risk level & message
  - Layman-friendly explanation
  - Recommendations & precautionary advice
- Modern, visually appealing interface that matches the landing page style.
- Ethical usage disclaimer and task instructions integrated.

---

## âš ï¸ Important Note

- **Only scan test/vulnerable sites** for demos and learning purposes.
- **Test Sites**:
  - [testphp.vulnweb.com](http://testphp.vulnweb.com)
  - [testhtml5.vulnweb.com](http://testhtml5.vulnweb.com)
  - DVWA (Damn Vulnerable Web App)
  - OWASP Juice Shop
- **Authorized testing only** for real sites (get permission first).

---

## ğŸ“ Demo / Presentation Instructions

1. Open the app in your browser.
2. Enter one of the **test sites** in the scanner input.
3. Observe the **radar animation** and **progress bar**.
4. Review the **results dashboard**, which highlights:
   - Vulnerabilities detected
   - Risk level (High, Medium, Low)
   - Clear explanations & recommendations
5. Explain how the scanner maps to **OWASP Top 10 vulnerabilities**:
   - SQL Injection â†’ A03
   - XSS â†’ A07
   - Weak headers â†’ A05
6. Emphasize **ethical scanning** only on authorized sites.

